OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776280294
OL,3,C3,000 jobs promised as nuclear power
OL,4,Cstation works begin
OL,6,FWork that's set to create 3000 jobs
OL,7,Fhas officially begun on the nuclear
OL,8,Fpower station project in Wylfa on
OL,9,FAnglesey.
OL,11,FThe UK Government has signed a key
OL,12,Fcontract that formally kicks off
OL,13,Fdesign of the UK's first "Small
OL,14,FModular Reactor" (SMR).
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
