OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776280294
OL,3,C3,000 jobs promised as nuclear power
OL,4,Cstation works begin
OL,6,FSmall Modular Reactors (SMR) are mini
OL,7,Fnuclear power stations which are
OL,8,Fsmaller and designed to be installed
OL,9,Fon site as prefabricated modules. SMRs
OL,10,Fshould be able to generate enough low-
OL,11,Fcarbon electricity to power the
OL,12,Fequivalent of around 3 million homes.
OL,14,FThe 21-acre Wylfa site is a twin
OL,15,Freactor decommissioning power station.
OL,16,FBuilt in the 1960s, the site closed in
OL,17,F2015, with de-fuelling completed four
OL,18,Fyears later.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776280294
OL,3,C3,000 jobs promised as nuclear power
OL,4,Cstation works begin
OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer officially
OL,7,Fannounced the project in November 2025
OL,8,Fpromising that "after years of
OL,9,Fneglect" his government will be
OL,10,F"cutting red tape, changing planning
OL,11,Flaws, and backing growth to deliver
OL,12,Fthe country's first SMR in north
OL,13,FWales."
OL,15,FRolls-Royce was selected as the
OL,16,Fpreferred company to undertake the
OL,17,Fworks in June 2025, and #2.6 billion
OL,18,Fwas allocated to deliver the project.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/8
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776280294
OL,3,C3,000 jobs promised as nuclear power
OL,4,Cstation works begin
OL,6,FThe first phase of the project is set
OL,7,Fto support around 3,000 local jobs at
OL,8,Fpeak construction.
OL,10,FChris Cholerton, Chief Executive of
OL,11,FRolls-Royce SMR, said: "This contract
OL,12,Funlocks the delivery of our first
OL,13,Fthree units and brings certainty to
OL,14,Fthe UK SMR programme...
OL,16,F"We are transforming the way nuclear
OL,17,Fprojects are delivered, to give
OL,18,Fgreater cost and schedule certainty
OL,19,Fwith a standardised, factory-built
OL,20,Fapproach.
OL,26,@sD@XOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
