FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776280294
OL,3,C3,000 jobs promised as nuclear power
OL,4,Cstation works begin
OL,6,F"This project is important to the UK's
OL,7,Fenergy security and will power up our
OL,8,Fbusiness and the UK supply chain, and
OL,9,Fwe are excited by the opportunity and
OL,10,Fare focused on successful delivery."
OL,12,FA history of nuclear on Anglesey
OL,14,FBuilt in the 1960s, Wylfa's nuclear
OL,15,Fpower station began operating in 1971,
OL,16,Frun by the company Magnox and
OL,17,Femploying thousands of workers. In
OL,18,F2006, its closure was scheduled for
OL,19,F2010.
OL,26,@rD@dO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
