OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1776280294
OL,3,C3,000 jobs promised as nuclear power
OL,4,Cstation works begin
OL,6,FIn 2023, Prime Minister Rishi Sunak,
OL,7,Ffurther designated Wylfa as one of the
OL,8,Fgovernment's preferred sites for a new
OL,9,Fnuclear power station.
OL,11,FWhilst in 2024, Chancellor Jeremy Hunt
OL,12,Fannounced a deal to purchase the Wylfa
OL,13,Fsite for a gigawatt nuclear power
OL,14,Fplant.
OL,16,FThis was shelved by Keir Starmer's
OL,17,FLabour government who instead chose
OL,18,Fthe site as the first site in the UK
OL,19,Ffor a Small Modular Reactor.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/8
